title: Critérium du Dauphiné stage 8: Jonas Vingegaard seals Tour de France primer as Giulio Ciccone wins out of break
content:
Vingegaard rides hot into Tour de France title defense with dominant overall victory in prestigious tune-up race, Ciccone scores out of breakaway raid.

Read the full article at Critérium du Dauphiné stage 8: Jonas Vingegaard seals Tour de France primer as Giulio Ciccone wins out of break on Velo.
